oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Tennessee's First Bicentennial Campus
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Cards; Basketball
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Chrisitan Brothers College was named the first Bicentennial Campus for Tennessee by the committee for the Bicentennial of the American Revolution, allowing the school to utilize the official logo of the Bicentennial during the year. This wallet card features the logo on one side and the basketball team's schedule for 1975-1976.
